605
00:46:01,217 --> 00:46:02,935
Oh, she was never happier

606
00:46:03,010 --> 00:46:04,853
than when she had
a paintbrush in her hand.

607
00:46:04,929 --> 00:46:06,351
That's right.

608
00:46:06,430 --> 00:46:10,435
She worked on this
one painting for days.

609
00:46:10,518 --> 00:46:13,488
