00:50:06,420 --> 00:50:07,467
He's good.

653
00:50:08,172 --> 00:50:09,264
Come on, Green!

654
00:50:11,842 --> 00:50:13,014
Eyes on the ball!

655
00:50:20,226 --> 00:50:21,728
Oh, dear God.

656
00:50:24,522 --> 00:50:25,694
