Come on. Hustle up!

659
00:50:33,405 --> 00:50:34,531
- Green.
- Nice job.

660
00:50:35,282 --> 00:50:36,454
Run, run, run!

661
00:50:37,910 --> 00:50:39,287
Don't cut any corners.

662
00:50:39,828 --> 00:50:41,171
