00:52:01,994 --> 00:52:03,337
Not what I had in mind, but...

700
00:52:03,412 --> 00:52:04,413
It's true.

701
00:52:04,496 --> 00:52:06,590
Okay! Keep your eye on the ball,

702
00:52:06,665 --> 00:52:08,963
