00:57:14,379 --> 00:57:15,505
- And you should.
- Well, good.

799
00:57:15,588 --> 00:57:19,809
Anyway, that Monday
was take your kid to work day.

800
00:57:20,552 --> 00:57:21,553
He started with me.

